snippet.title: Live Coding: Learning Dart from Scratch
snippet.description:
Dart is starting to gain a lot of hype because of the Flutter framework that is available for making cross-platform native mobile applications. Dart is a language from Google that looks like it will be easy to pick up at first glance, having similar syntax to C++ and Java. Let's get to know the language and how it works, how to install and compile, and start building a cookbook. This will prepare us to start making mobile apps using Flutter!
